issue.title: [Tracking] Falco 0.36.2
issue.body:
# Falco 0.36.2 Release

Will keep this issue updated with the current status and progress.

## Date

Release date: 2023-10-27

## Release Steps

The process is described in [this document](https://github.com/falcosecurity/falco/blob/master/RELEASE.md).

```[tasklist]
## Release Blocking PRs and issues
- [x] [Falco 0.36.2 milestone](https://github.com/falcosecurity/falco/milestone/36)
- [x] [Libs 0.13.4 milestone](https://github.com/falcosecurity/libs/milestone/31)
```

```[tasklist]
## External dependencies
- [x] falcoctl -> Not needed
- [x] libs https://github.com/falcosecurity/libs/releases/tag/0.13.4
- [x] drivers -> Not needed
- [x] rules -> Not needed
- [x] plugins -> Not needed
- [x] charts -> https://github.com/falcosecurity/charts/pull/570
```

## Action Items

- [x] **Pre-Release**
  - [x]  Milestone -> https://github.com/falcosecurity/falco/milestone/36
  - [x] Code freeze in falcosecurity/falco
  - [x] Open release branch in Falco and protect it
  - [x] See `External dependencies` task lists
  - [x] Prebuilt drivers publish
  - [x] Code thaw in falcosecurity/falco
- [x] **Release**
  - [x] Github Release in the Falco repo
- [x] **Website**
  - [x] Create new snapshot
    - [x] Protect snapshot branch
  - [x] Merge all necessary PRs
- [ ] **Announcements**
  - [ ] mailing list 
  - [x] blog post -> https://github.com/falcosecurity/falco-website/pull/1191
  - [ ] slack channel
- [ ] **Post-Release**
  - [x] Update supported fields and syscall documentation
  - [ ] Archive community call meeting notes
  - [x] Changelog

## Miscs

/milestone 0.36.2

/assign @FedeDP

/kind documentation

---

# Falco 0.36.2 Release

Will keep this issue updated with the current status and progress.

## Date

Release date: 2023-13-03

## Release Steps

The process is described in [this document](https://github.com/falcosecurity/falco/blob/master/RELEASE.md).

```[tasklist]
## Release Blocking PRs and issues
- [x] [Falco 0.36.2 milestone](https://github.com/falcosecurity/falco/milestone/36)
- [x] [Libs 0.13.4 milestone](https://github.com/falcosecurity/libs/milestone/31)
```

```[tasklist]
## External dependencies
- [x] falcoctl -> Not needed
- [x] libs https://github.com/falcosecurity/libs/releases/tag/0.13.4
- [x] drivers -> Not needed
- [x] rules -> Not needed
- [x] plugins -> Not needed
- [x] charts -> https://github.com/falcosecurity/charts/pull/570
```

## Action Items

- [x] **Pre-Release**
  - [x]  Milestone -> https://github.com/falcosecurity/falco/milestone/36
  - [x] Code freeze in falcosecurity/falco
  - [x] Open release branch in Falco and protect it
